  WE RECOMEND INSTALING THIS GAME ON THE HARD DRIVE

  How to install ? It's easy.
  When you have unpacked a archive CyberBlast2.lha there is icon called
  'InstallMe' in main catalog of the archive.
  Just click on it and response for few question just like where the game
  want you to install if you want to install on floppy or hard drive.
  If you decided to install on floppy renember that the installer will be
  on third disk 'CyberIII' in main catalog and you have to make some
  changes in file 'startup-sequence' which you can find on first disk
  called 'Cyber' in drawer 's'.
  These chaneges are installing valid for your country keymap and command
   'setpatch'
  This is example of startup-sequence:

  setpatch
  setmap se
  engine
  
  In drawer 'devs/keymaps' must be definition of keybord (e.x: se, gb) 
  and in drawer 'c' must be commmand 'setpatch' and 'setmap'.
  To drawer 'devs' you can copy file 'system-configuration' but it is 
  not necessary.
  If you are playing from hard drive the game uses your system's settings
  such as keymap.

  THE GAME USES EXTRA MEMORY IF SUCH IS AVAILABLE.


